# Docker build-context excludes.
#
# WHY THIS FILE EXISTS (2026-07-17): all three built services (control-plane, scheduler,
# telegram-bridge) share control-plane/Dockerfile with `context: .` — the REPO ROOT — because the
# Dockerfile COPYs pods/ + prompts/ + scripts/ alongside control-plane/. With no .dockerignore the
# build context was the ENTIRE project, including volumes/ — whose postgres data is owned by the
# container's uid. A non-root `docker compose build` then dies before it starts:
#     checking context: can't stat '/volume1/docker/jarvis/volumes/postgres'
# (It only "worked" before when run under sudo.) Excluding volumes/ fixes that permanently, and
# dropping the trees the Dockerfile never copies makes the context tiny instead of gigabytes.
#
# ⚠ KEEP IN SYNC WITH control-plane/Dockerfile's COPY list. These must NOT be excluded:
#     control-plane/  ·  pods/  ·  scripts/  ·  prompts/  ·  companion/telegram-bridge.mjs

# ── the build breaker: runtime bind-mounts (root/container-owned) ────────────────────────────────
volumes/

# ── vcs, deps, build output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git/
.gitattributes
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dev-dist/

# ── secrets + local machine state: never bake these into an image (env comes from compose) ───────
.env
.env.*
.claude/
*.log
control-plane/data/

# ── work product + local ledgers (regenerated at runtime; not needed to build) ───────────────────
gov-drafts/
fiverr-assets/
tax-inbox/
tax-docs/
tax-ledger/
finance-credit/
ideas-vault/
reports/

# ── big trees the Dockerfile never COPYs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
jarvis-world/
dealforge/
desktop/
hq/
site/
web-templates/
docs/
evals/
n8n/
Biography/
UI Inspiration/

# ── companion/: the image COPYs exactly one file from here (companion/telegram-bridge.mjs). We do
# NOT do an exclude-then-negate dance on the folder — a negation slip would break that COPY and cost a
# build cycle. Keeping the (small) source dir in context is cheap; just drop its heavy artifacts.
companion/public/models/
companion/public/_generated/
companion/desktop/
companion/.usage.json
companion/.dashboard.json
